    <title>Hexo基本操作</title>
    <url>/2020/03/10/hexo%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-Hexo添加menu中的分类-标签等"><a href="#1-Hexo添加menu中的分类-标签等" class="headerlink" title="1. Hexo添加menu中的分类/标签等"></a>1. Hexo添加menu中的分类/标签等</h2><p>博客最基本的需求就是对博文进行分类，初始化的Hexo只有首页和归档，如何进行添加呢？</p>
<ol>
<li>新建<figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new<span class="built_in"> page </span>categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
这样会在/Hexo/source新建categories文件夹，里边包含index.md</li>
<li>处理index.md<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">categories</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="number">2017</span><span class="number">-12</span><span class="number">-02</span> <span class="number">21</span><span class="string">:01:24</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">"categories"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
在其中加入type字段即可</li>
</ol>
<a id="more"></a>

<ol start="3">
<li>处理<strong>主题</strong>配置文件<figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">menu:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  home:</span> / || home</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="meta">#about: /about/ || user</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  tags:</span> <span class="meta-keyword">/tags/</span> || tags</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  categories:</span> <span class="meta-keyword">/categories/</span> || th</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  archives:</span> <span class="meta-keyword">/archives/</span> || archive</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="meta">#schedule: /schedule/ || calendar</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="meta">#sitemap: /sitemap.xml || sitemap</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="meta">#commonweal: /404/ || heartbeat</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
将其中的注释删除</li>
<li>重新部署<figure class="highlight sas"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean <span class="variable">&amp;&amp;</span> hexo g <span class="variable">&amp;&amp;</span> hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="2-发布博文"><a href="#2-发布博文" class="headerlink" title="2. 发布博文"></a>2. 发布博文</h2><ol>
<li>git bash新建 <figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>new "文章名称"```</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">\Hexo\source\_posts会出现相关的文章名称.md文件</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">2. 修改.md文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<p>title: title #文章標題<br>date: 2016-06-01 23:47:44 #文章生成時間<br>categories: “Hexo教程” #文章分類目錄 可以省略<br>tags: #文章標籤 可以省略<br>     - 标签1<br>     - 标签2<br> description: #你對本頁的描述 可以省略</p>
<hr>
<figure class="highlight clean"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">初始化只有title和data，添加categories和tags即可</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">3.</span> 撰写/保存/部署</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">其中不要忘记加入```&lt;!-- more --&gt;```进行摘要展示</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">###### 所以说文章分类和文章标签只需要自己在写文章时加入，部署时自动生成</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">## <span class="number">3.</span> 常用的MD语法</span><br><span class="line">###### MD用的少，word与latex比较熟悉，所以记录一下常用的</span><br><span class="line">#### 标记与多重标记</span><br><span class="line">使用&gt;与&gt;&gt;表示标记</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&gt; 标记里再使用 </span><br><span class="line">&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&gt; &gt; 标记</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#### 多级标题</span><br><span class="line">使用<span class="number">1</span><span class="number">-6</span>个#表示多级标题</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#### 列表</span><br><span class="line">+-*表示无序列表</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">* 我的微信公众号</span><br><span class="line">* 我的微信公众号</span><br><span class="line">* 我的微信公众号</span><br><span class="line">- 我的尾巴</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">数字加英文.表示有序列表</span><br><span class="line">#### 分割线</span><br><span class="line">分割线可以由* - _（星号，减号，底线）这<span class="number">3</span>个符号的至少<span class="number">3</span>个符号表示，注意至少要<span class="number">3</span>个，且不需要连续，有空格也可以</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">*******</span><br><span class="line">#### 链接</span><br><span class="line">链接的文字放在[]中，链接地址放在随后的（）中</span><br><span class="line">[我的知乎](https:<span class="comment">//www.zhihu.com/people/liu-hao-33-54)</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#### 图片</span><br><span class="line">与链接基本一致，加入！即可</span><br><span class="line">![微信](https:<span class="comment">//raw.githubusercontent.com/smshen/MarkdownPhotos/master/Res/test.jpg)</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#### 强调</span><br><span class="line">\*倾斜\*   </span><br><span class="line">\*\*加粗\*\*</span><br><span class="line">\~\~删除\~\~</span><br><span class="line">*倾斜*</span><br><span class="line">**加粗**</span><br><span class="line">~~删除~~</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#### 转义</span><br><span class="line">和latex等都差不多，用\即可</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#### 代码</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">如果代码量比较少，只有单行的话，可以用单反引号包起来，如下：</span><br><span class="line">`asd`</span><br><span class="line">如果多行就用</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">```c++</span><br><span class="line">int main&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	vector&lt;int&gt; temp;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="comment">//...</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
